Tsukine OS
================================

This is a personal Linux distribution for music creators, built on Linux 6.6.

Current version: indev-0.1.0
Goal: A lightweight, controllable environment for UTAU / Vocaloid production.

System avatar: 津時 (Tsutoki) — a gray wolf with heterochromia.

Own tools:
  - tsukine_top      : task manager
  - tsukine_net      : network config
  - tsukine_net_ui   : network monitor

